</div><br class="clear"><div class="gallery__next" style="display:none;"><h2 class="gallery__next-heading">NEXT GALLERY: <a href="the-best-moisturisers-for-oily-skin.html" title="The best moisturisers for oily skin">The best moisturisers for oily skin >>></a></h2></div></div><div class="gallery__column gallery__column--text"><div class="gallery__counter">1 / 11</div><div class="gallery__text-wrapper" ><h3 class="gallery__item-title">The Gloss Report: Trainers</h3><div class="description gallery__intro"><div id="shortDescription1" class="gallery__intro--short"><p>Which trainers actually do what they promise?&nbsp;</p>
<p>Whether you're looking for a new shoe to wear to the gym, walk to work or something more suited to running, we've tested through the latest launches and let you in on what we actually thought.</p>
<p>Click through the gallery for our honest reviews...&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div></div><a name="slide-2" class="gallery__anchor"></a><div class="gallery__item"><div class="gallery__column gallery__column--image"><div class="gallery__image"><img class="lazy" data-original="https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/b9gtglive/public/image/nike-21.jpg" alt="Nike Metcon DSX Flyknit Women's Training Shoe, £125"></div><div class="desktopSocial"><div class="social">
	<ul>
		<li class="facebookIcon"> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgetthegloss.com%2Fgallery%2Fthe-gloss-report-trainers%23slide-2&amp;t=The+Gloss+Report%3A+Trainers" target="_blank"></a> </li>
